'''Alastair Neil Duncan''' (born [[29 January|January 29]], [[1958]]) is a Scottish voice actor.
==Roles==
* [[2017]]: ''[[Middle-earth: Shadow of War]]'' - [[Celebrimbor|Wraith]]
* [[2014]]: ''[[Middle-earth: Shadow of Mordor]]'' - [[Celebrimbor|Wraith]]
* [[2003]]: ''[[The Hobbit (2003 video game)|The Hobbit]]'' - [[Kíli]], Additional voices

==Awards==
* [[2015]] - '''[https://www.behindthevoiceactors.com/ BTVA Award]''', Best Male Vocal Performance in a Video Game in a Supporting Role, ''[[Middle-earth: Shadow of Mordor]]''
